# Build and Deployment

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite bundler configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [tailwind.config.mjs](mdc:tailwind.config.mjs) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [wrangler.toml](mdc:wrangler.toml) - Cloudflare Workers configuration

## Build Process

The project uses Vite for building and Cloudflare Pages for deployment. Serverless functions are deployed as Cloudflare Workers.
